/20090814/13097130</a></blockquote><br />\n包龍星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔醒目點會屌到條咁正既女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係醒目，但條女好正咩？"},{"pid":"3df1b9546ab9f7a06ecc592dfcb6f5d4735cdc12","tid":423902,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"其實條女改過口供<br />\n你地無人記得咩<br />\n一開頭係話自願搞野不願拍片<br />\n如果真係強既就唔會咁耐之後流出左條片先告啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbd2d9bd14319a738e6e78857d5883b0f6deb54","tid":423902,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"09年判得4年<br />\n一早出返黎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又可以繼續做男主角"},{"pid":"6ec9d76abe4e080c4b8f46493c727ed0846f577f","tid":423902,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"當年判左幾多年"},{"pid":"2608cf2b6fde09a359a97fc36c0c85e8ad179254","tid":423902,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"原來得4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2743c43e3914431be3126495cc8bce7667f3576","tid":423902,"uid":47877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"有無得重溫條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddfa8b2a7d1b360b648aae6be731b40cdb72fc8","tid":423902,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"Jed"},{"pid":"37993ef3c1ba4a40726f1d4af4c0fc876cd606f3","tid":423902,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>瞄撚準未</blockquote><br />\n瞄撚準備</blockquote><br />\n條撚好味</blockquote><br />\n搖撚準備</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\